=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
*ירא    - ירה / yârâh  yârâ' / yaw-raw', yaw-raw'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
properly to flow as water (that is, to [[rain]]); transitively to lay or throw (especially an arrow, that is, to shoot); figuratively to point out (as if by aiming the finger), to teach: -  (+) archer, cast, direct, inform, instruct, lay, shew, shoot, teach (-er, -ing), through.
[[fr:ירה]]